{"tid":2383461,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"洪卓立結咗婚未？","createTime":"2021-01-28T02:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T02:37:47.000Z","uid":137896,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b613ab4e50e5f28c1cd900cd6598e6a4ded3ac0f","tid":2383461,"uid":137896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"洪卓立（Ken）昨日到柴灣出席《聖誕環遊英倫》亮燈活動，他透露目前正為新碟錄音，希望明年2月推出新歌，內容將會跟其女友湯怡有關。<br />\n<br />\n明年是Ken入行十周年，他想寫一首歌作總結，由於當年他曾經大病一場入院，Ken感激女友從沒有離開他，並大讚湯怡條件很好，直認已視她為結婚對象，笑言：「<span class=\"green\">除非佢唔要我啦，否則打算在近幾年結婚。</span>」今年聖誕節，他計劃在家中開派對，並準備送一些遊戲機給女友，順道訓練她的膽量。<br />\n<br />\n攝影：林良明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1633637/洪卓立非湯怡不娶\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1633637%2F%E6%B4%AA%E5%8D%93%E7%AB%8B%E9%9D%9E%E6%B9%AF%E6%80%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%A8%B6&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=e24af8e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1633637/洪卓立非湯怡不娶</a>"},{"pid":"7f133f0a8886c079fc75e7518a1948cf7c517f03","tid":2383461,"uid":82752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:37:47.000Z","msg":"條死臭雞湯怡話鳩黃腳立無錢結婚擺酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}